				\begin{document}$$\begin{aligned} glm \, (mycoperc\,\sim \,soil.origin \, * \, plant.origin \, \quad * \, drought \, * \, inoculum\, + \,block, \, family \\ \, & = \,quasibinomial) \\ \end{aligned}$$\end{document}glm(mycoperc∼soil.origin∗plant.origin∗drought∗inoculum+block,family=quasibinomial)
